videos.description: Purdue wide receiver Isaac Zico makes the spectacular one-handed 13-yard touchdown catch.
videos.headline: Purdue WR makes one-handed TD catch

videos.description: Purdue sophomore Tyler Trent is just 20 years old and in hospice care, but he wouldn't let that stop him from taking in the Boilermakers' game against Ohio State.
videos.headline: Purdue's No. 1 fan defies the odds to attend game

videos.description: Purdue's Rondale Moore gets the pass from David Blough and speeds his way to the end zone giving Purdue a 14-3 lead right before half.
videos.headline: Purdue extends lead with 9-yard TD

videos.description: Purdue's David Blough throws two touchdowns in the first half, one after a fake field goal and the Boilermakers hold a 14-3 lead.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Purdue up on No. 2 OSU at the half) 2018/10/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Purdue up on No. 2 OSU at the half

videos.description: Purdue running back D.J. Knox follows his blocks and powers his way into the end zone for the 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Purdue RB powers into end zone for TD

videos.description: Purdue running back D.J. Knox gets the handoff and takes off for 42 yards, giving Purdue a 28-6 fourth-quarter lead.
videos.headline: Purdue RB takes off for 42-yard TD run

videos.description: Purdue's D.J. Knox takes the handoff and explodes through the hole scoring the 40-yard TD.
videos.headline: Purdue's Knox scores 3rd TD of the day

videos.description: Rondale Moore catches the pass and breaks numerous tackles en route to a 43-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Purdue's Moore breaks multiple tackles to score TD

videos.description: Purdue sophomore Tyler Trent, who is battling cancer is interviewed by Tom Rinaldi after Purdue takes a big lead over Ohio State.
videos.headline: Tyler Trent is pumped about Purdue leading Ohio State

videos.description: Purdue puts up a rout of Ohio State, scoring 28 points in the fourth quarter to send the Buckeyes to their first loss.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Purdue stuns undefeated Ohio State) 2018/10/20 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Purdue stuns undefeated Ohio State

videos.description: Purdue's Markus Bailey picks off Dwayne Haskins and returns it 41 yards for the pick-6.
videos.headline: Purdue gets game-sealing pick-6

videos.description: Purdue head coach Jeff Brohm talks with Maria Taylor about his team's win over Ohio State and the inspiration his team gets from Tyler Trent.
videos.headline: Aggressive from the start

videos.description: Kirk Herbstreit joins SVP on SportsCenter to break down Ohio State's issues following a loss to Purdue.
